// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0886 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: acbbb6fa-7dd8-59bf-81ac-989da512e49c

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
